<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٥ - <span class="c2">(١٢١١)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4085">عَبْدُ الْوَهَّابِ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6932">يَحْيَى بْنَ سَعِيدٍ </a>يَقُولُ: أَخْبَرَتْنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4781">عَمْرَةُ </a>أَنَّهَا سَمِعَتْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> <span class="c2">(ح)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>